00:58:34,990 --> 00:58:36,100
Sungguh?

954
00:58:36,700 --> 00:58:39,700
Tapi hanya sedikit?

955
00:58:40,530 --> 00:58:41,930
Itu tidak mungkin.

956
00:58:42,100 --> 00:58:43,800
Coba lihat lebih dekat.

957
00:58:43,800 --> 00:58:45,930
Pasti akan kelihatan banyak.
Lihatlah.

958
00:58:45,930 --> 00:58:47,310
Menjijikkan sekali.
Hentikan.

959
00:58:47,310 --> 00:58:50,240
Lihat saja. Lihat seberapa besar
rasa peduliku padamu.

960
00:58:50,240 --> 00:58:51,310
Lihat.

961
00:58:51,310 --> 00:58:53,410
Apa kau bercanda lagi sekarang?

962
00:59:11,800 --> 00:59:12,930
Mereka kelihatan cocok.

963
00:59:13,660 --> 00:59:15,060
Memang.

964
00:59:15,260 --> 00:59:18,830
Kenapa mereka sering banget bertengkar
kalau saling sayang sampai sebegitunya?

965
00:59:20,010 --> 00:59:22,780
Jadi, mau ke restoran sekarang?

966
00:59:23,030 --> 00:59:24,050
Baiklah.

967
00:59:24,050 --> 00:59:25,510
Baiklah. Aku yang traktir.

968
00:59:30,580 --> 00:59:31,720
Aduh, aku lapar sekali.

969
00:59:32,280 --> 00:59:34,910
Soo Ah, apa kau tidak lapar?

970
00:59:35,490 --> 00:59:37,220
Aku lapar sedikit.

971
00:59:37,430 --> 00:59:40,830
Benarkah? Kalau begitu apa kau mau
cari restoran yang nyaman..

972
00:59:41,100 --> 00:59:42,260
dan makan di sana?

973
00:59:44,390 --> 00:59:47,530
Berdua saja?

974
00:59:47,560 --> 00:59:48,600
Kenapa?

975
00:59:49,060 --> 00:59:52,740
Memangnya ada alasan kenapa teman
tidak boleh makan berduaan?

976
00:59:55,140 --> 00:59:56,280
Benar.

977
00:59:58,200 --> 01:00:02,080
Tapi, di mana restoran nyaman yang
kau maksud itu?

978
01:00:02,620 --> 01:00:05,350
Baiklah, ayo keluar dan kita cari saja.

979
01:00:08,260 --> 01:00:09,490
Ayo.

980
01:00:32,600 --> 01:00:35,180
Kenapa tidak ada orang di rumah?
Aneh sekali.

981
01:00:42,780 --> 01:00:45,330
Halo, ini Penginapan Waikiki.

982
01:00:45,890 --> 01:00:46,890
Ya.

983
01:00:48,330 --> 01:00:50,720
Apa? Dong Gu?

984
01:00:51,430 --> 01:00:53,660
Ya, baiklah. Aku mengerti.

985
01:00:57,970 --> 01:00:59,710
(Dong Gu)

986
01:01:12,380 --> 01:01:14,950
Dong Gu, apa lagi ini?

987
01:01:29,190 --> 01:01:30,900
Apa yang kau lakukan?

988
01:01:32,260 --> 01:01:33,330
Yoon Ah.

